Altshift Framework package for nodejs

DESCRIPTION:

This the altshift framework for nodejs. The aim is to gather the best npm packages through 
dependencies and provide functions and classes relying on JS.Class (http://jsclass.jcoglan.com/).

HOW TO INSTALL:

 1. Install plugin `git clone git://github.com/as-jpolo/altshift.git .` OR install via npm `npm install altshift` 
 2. Include the library in your path

